== 人口 ==
[[File:St-Helena-Jamestown-from-above.jpg|thumb]]
截至2016年，詹姆斯敦共有629名居民<ref name="census2016">{{cite web|title=St Helena 2016 Population & Housing: Census Summary Report|url=http://www.sainthelena.gov.sh/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Census-2016-Summary-Report.pdf|website=Census 2016|publisher=St Helena Statistics Office|accessdate=2016-11-21|page=12|archive-date=2016-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017192624/http://www.sainthelena.gov.sh/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Census-2016-summary-report.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，相较2008年的714人有显著下降<ref name="census2008">{{cite web |url=http://www.sainthelena.gov.sh/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Census-Report-2008.pdf |format=PDF |title=2008 Population Census of St Helena |publisher=St Helena Government |date= |accessdate=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228025431/http://www.sainthelena.gov.sh/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Census-Report-2008.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。詹姆斯敦人口常年缩减，已非全岛最大居民点，半树谷、{{le|圣保罗 (圣赫勒拿)|Saint Paul's, Saint Helena|圣保罗}}及朗伍德人口均多于詹姆斯敦<ref name="census2016"/>。

== 教育 ==
作为英国殖民地，圣赫勒拿采用[[英国教育|英国教育]]系统。詹姆斯敦有一所小学——皮林小学，2007年9月由詹姆斯敦第一学校及皮林中学合并而成<ref>{{cite web|title=Pilling Primary School: Value for Money Report|url=http://audit.gov.sh/publications/vfm_pilling_primary_%20school_report_final.pdf|website=St Helena Audit Service|publisher=|accessdate=2016-11-21|page=3|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305004824/http://audit.gov.sh/publications/vfm_pilling_primary_%20school_report_final.pdf|archive-date=2017-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，供四岁至十一岁儿童就学
<ref>{{cite web|title=Education and Employment|url=http://www.sainthelena.gov.sh/education-and-employment/|website=St Helena|accessdate=2016-11-21|date=2013-02-02|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503222907/http://www.sainthelena.gov.sh/education-and-employment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。全岛唯一[[中学|中学]]为安德鲁王子学校，位于圣保罗而非詹姆斯敦<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Paul’s|url=http://sainthelenaisland.info/stpauls.htm|website=sainthelenaisland.info|accessdate=2016-11-21|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503223050/http://sainthelenaisland.info/stpauls.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 宗教 ==
[[File:Church059_Anglican-St_James'_Church_Jamestown.jpg|thumb]]
圣詹姆斯堂区为圣公宗圣赫勒拿教区三个堂区之一。圣詹姆斯教堂为堂区首要教堂，为南半球最古老的圣公宗教堂，现存建筑建于1772年。詹姆斯敦亦有三个次要教堂，分别为位于上詹姆斯敦的圣约翰教堂、位于布莱尔的圣玛丽教堂及位于鲁珀特谷的圣迈克尔教堂<ref name=anglican>{{cite web|title=The Diocese of St Helena|url=http://www.dioceseofsthelena.com/|website=www.dioceseofsthelena.com|accessdate=2016-11-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710130456/http://www.dioceseofsthelena.com/|archivedate=2011-07-10|df=}}</ref>。圣赫勒拿岛唯一天主教教堂——圣心教堂<ref>{{cite web|title=Church of the Sacred Heart, Jamestown, Saint Helena, Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha|url=http://www.gcatholic.org/churches/islands/15616.htm|website=www.gcatholic.org|accessdate=2016-11-21|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503222641/http://www.gcatholic.org/churches/islands/15616.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>及唯一的[[浸礼宗|浸礼宗]]教堂亦位于詹姆斯敦<ref>{{cite web|title=Churches of St Helena|url=http://sainthelenaisland.info/churches.htm|website=sainthelenaisland.info|accessdate=2016-11-21|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503221626/http://sainthelenaisland.info/churches.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
